headline: This Incredible Dividend Growth Stock's Hidden AI Story Could Deliver 20% Annual Returns
summary: The market is completely missing what's happening at S&P Global (NYSE: SPGI).  While investors obsess over the latest artificial intelligence (AI) start-up or trendy tech stock, this 165-year-old financial data powerhouse is quietly orchestrating one of the most compelling margin expansion stories in the market.  The combination of an upcoming business spinoff, aggressive AI integration, and a management team that's already proved it can achieve 50.9% GAAP operating margins creates a setup that could deliver double-digit annual returns for the next 10 years.
